        "action": "Ban routine overbooking on UK flights",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "We call on the Government to introduce a ban on routine overbooking of flights. Every day, thousands of flights are overbooked and as a result, many consumers are left at a massive inconvenience. We ask for a legal ban of this practice.",
